{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a88501868f","title":"在中央组织部七月份综合报告上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a4e116ea86","index":0,"year":1962,"month":8,"day":12,"articleId":"a88501868f"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"40921d8cfa","type":"title","text":"在中央组织部七月份综合报告上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a88501868f"},{"id":"6aed8e3971","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a88501868f"},{"id":"6aa94ba131","type":"paragraph","text":"印发各同志。中央组织部从来不向中央作报告，以致中央同志对组织部同志们的活动一无所知，全部封锁，成了一个独立王国。现在部长安子文同志在经过批评之后，觉悟了，这就好了。希望毛病不要重犯。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a88501868f"}],"page":{"id":"bc009e1c15","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"a88501868f","start":0,"end":0}},"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"56bfbeb1b8","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"a88501868f","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指当时正在北戴河参加中共中央工作会议的同志。"}],"contents":[{"id":"38d2df4360","type":"title","text":"在中央组织部七月份综合报告“上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"a88501868f"},{"id":"56bfbeb1b8","type":"paragraph","text":"印发各同志”。中央组织部从来不向中央作报告，以致中央同志对组织部同志们的活动一无所知，全部封锁，成了一个独立王国。现在部长安子文同志在经过批评之后，觉悟了，这就好了。希望毛病不要重犯。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"a88501868f"},{"id":"7857ba8651","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]中共中央组织部在1962年7月29日给毛泽东、中央政治局常委的7月份综合报告中检讨说，长期以来，没有向主席和常委报告工作，反映情况，这是一个严重的错误。今后，一定引以为戒，努力改正。报告主要讲干部队伍方面的情况和问题。认为在干部队伍方面，有两个问题值得注意，一是一部分干部的精神状态不正常，二是千部队伍过于庞大。报告对解决这两个同题提出了具体意见。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"a88501868f"},{"id":"abf7df30d1","type":"paragraph","text":"八月十二日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"a88501868f"},{"id":"b476ff0305","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"a88501868f"}],"page":{"id":"f7e0efe963","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"a88501868f","start":203,"end":203}}}},"__N_SSG":true}